x4freetext: Targets were manufactured at electromagnetic separator
by implantation of 29Si ions accelerated up to the
energy of 25 keV into thick backings. Tantalum was used
as a backing material for (p,g) and (p,p`g)  reactions.
Graphite backings were used for investigation of
elastic scattering. Target thicknesses corresponded to
a 2 keV loss  for protons with the energy of 3 MeV.
